      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>beef mince</strong> and <strong>onion wedges </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking the mince up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
