    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to brown, add the<strong> sliced carrot</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and cook for a further 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>",
