    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef and veg are cooking, dissolve your<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
